<title>CHINA: Shanghai Petrochem gets 300 mln yuan loan quota.</title>
<headline>Shanghai Petrochem gets 300 mln yuan loan quota.</headline>
<dateline>SHANGHAI 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shanghai Petrochemical Co Ltd has obtained a 300 million yuan ($36.1 million) loan quota for 1997 from the Shanghai-based Bank of Communications, the Shanghai Securities News said on Tuesday.</p>
<p>Bank of Communications will loan Shanghai Petrochemical 300 million yuan during the remainder of the year for use as working capital, the newspaper said.</p>
<p>It gave no other details of the loan agreement.</p>
